<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Dear <%= @user.name %>,</h1>
    <p>
      	We have recently detected that student: <% student.name %>
		has been absent over <%= student.attendances.count(:conditions => { :absent => true}) %>
		times this semester.<br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      This student exceeds the number of allowed absences
    </p>
    <p>Thank you and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>